PrecisAmendment to the YUKON QUARTZ MINING ACT WORK RELIEF REGULATIONS (1979) extending for a period of two years relief from the legislated work requirements for mineral claim holders in an area of the northern Yukon Territory extending from the Beaufort Sea to the Porcupine and Bell Rivers and from Alaska to the Northwest Territories.

precis:
Amendment to the YUKON QUARTZ MINING ACT WORK RELIEF REGULATIONS (1979)
extending for a period of two years relief from the legislated work
requirements for mineral claim holders in an area of the northern Yukon
Territory extending from the Beaufort Sea to the Porcupine and Bell Rivers
and from Alaska to the Northwest Territories.
